1.query:
fetch logs
| search("n8n.audit.workflow.created")
| parse content, "JSON:json_content"
| fields timestamp, json_content[`eventName`], json_content[`payload`][`_email`], json_content[`payload`][`workflowId`], json_content[`payload`][`workflowName`]
| fieldsAdd workflowLink = concat($n8n_root_url, `json_content[payload][workflowId]`)
| makeTimeseries count(), by: {`json_content[payload][workflowName]`, workflowLink}

4.query:
fetch logs
| search("n8n.audit.workflow.created")
| parse content, "JSON:json_content"
| fields timestamp, `creator email` = json_content[`payload`][`_email`], `id` = json_content[`payload`][`workflowId`], `name` = json_content[`payload`][`workflowName`]
| fieldsAdd `workflow link` = concat("[", `name`, "](", concat($n8n_root_url, "/workflow/",`id`), ")")

9.title: Successful Workflow Runs
9.query:
fetch logs
| search("n8n.workflow.success")
| parse content, "JSON:json_content"
| fields timestamp, json_content[`payload`][`executionId`], json_content[`payload`][`workflowId`], json_content[`payload`][`isManual`], json_content[`payload`][`workflowName`]
| fieldsAdd `execution link` = concat("[link](", concat($n8n_root_url, "/workflow/",`json_content[payload][workflowId]`, "/executions/", `json_content[payload][executionId]`), ")")
| summarize count(), by: {`json_content[payload][workflowName]`}

10.query:
fetch logs
| search("n8n.audit.workflow.archived")
| parse content, "JSON:json_content"
| fields timestamp, json_content[`eventName`], json_content[`payload`][`_email`], json_content[`payload`][`workflowId`], json_content[`payload`][`workflowName`]
| fieldsAdd workflowLink = concat($n8n_root_url, `json_content[payload][workflowId]`)
| makeTimeseries count(), by: {`json_content[payload][workflowName]`, workflowLink}
